---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="简历 - 刘扬">
  <main class="page-body">
    <article class="paper">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="masthead">
        <div class="header-row">
          <div class="header-main">
            <span class="masthead-label">Résumé</span>
            <h1 class="name">刘扬</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="photo-wrapper">
            <div class="photo" style="background-image: url('/avatar-small.jpg');"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-row">
          <span class="contact-item">132-0291-3900</span>
          <span class="contact-divider">·</span>
          <span class="contact-item">leoyoung_work@outlook.com</span>
          <span class="contact-divider">·</span>
          <span class="contact-item">微信: LeoYoung_H</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Education -->
      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">教育背景</h2>
        <div class="edu-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <span class="org">汕头大学 · 网络与新媒体</span>
            <span class="date">2021.09 – 2026.06</span>
          </div>
          <p class="edu-detail">学业成绩：总 GPA <span class="hl">4.01 / 5</span> · <span class="hl">专业排名第一</span></p>
          <p class="courses">相关课程：用户研究方法 · 问卷调查与统计分析 · 传播统计学 · 数据库原理与技术 · Python 数据挖掘</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Projects -->
      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">项目经验</h2>
        
        <div class="project-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <div class="org-group">
              <span class="org">潮博AR数字人</span>
              <span class="tag">AR + AI / 组长</span>
            </div>
            <span class="date">2024</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-subtitle">数字人技术在文旅领域的创新应用 · <a href="https://www.douyin.com/video/7384718579020746038" target="_blank" class="link">抖音视频</a></p>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li><strong>用户研究：</strong>主导前期调研，收集 500+ 有效问卷并进行用户行为分析，精准定位游客在博物馆导览中的交互痛点。</li>
            <li><strong>AI 训练：</strong>构建 50 万字潮汕文博知识库，基于 Convai 平台训练数字人性格与专业知识，实现智能化文旅讲解与行程规划。</li>
            <li><strong>技术开发：</strong>集成 Unity、Google AR Services 与 3D 建模技术，实现数字人在实境中的稳定放置与多模态交互。</li>
            <li><strong>项目成果：</strong>在汕头市博物馆、潮博中心进行试点应用，打造城市文旅 IP 形象名片，获显著社会效益与推广潜力。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="project-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <div class="org-group">
              <span class="org">春日寻英迹</span>
              <span class="tag">红色文创</span>
            </div>
            <span class="date">2023 – 2024</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-subtitle">“红动粤东”红色文化文创产品设计与开发</p>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li><strong>产品矩阵：</strong>主导设计种子明信片、英烈群像卡片、红色文旅套装（餐具、茶具、护照、钥匙扣）等多元文创产品。</li>
            <li><strong>叙事传播：</strong>立足粤东红色资源，通过Q版及立绘风格形象化表达英烈故事，结合现代审美打造沉浸式文博体验。</li>
            <li><strong>文旅融合：</strong>将文化内涵与生活实用需求深度结合，产品助力青年与红色文化的连接，获多篇微信公众号专题报道。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="project-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <div class="org-group">
              <span class="org">Wisdio</span>
              <span class="tag">独立产品</span>
            </div>
            <span class="date">2024 – 2026</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-subtitle">基于 LLM 的视频学习浏览器插件 · <a href="https://wisdio.org" target="_blank" class="link">wisdio.org</a></p>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li><strong>痛点拆解：</strong>针对长视频学习中"低效试错、提取关键信息难"等痛点，主导设计 AI 浏览器插件。</li>
            <li><strong>产品设计：</strong>梳理核心业务流程，设计支持自定义 Prompt、Markdown 实时预览的交互原型。</li>
            <li><strong>项目成果：</strong>适配桌面端及移动端，实现端到端视频对话，正进行灰度测试。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="project-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <div class="org-group">
              <span class="org">Grammar Check</span>
              <span class="tag">独立产品设计</span>
            </div>
            <span class="date">2024</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-subtitle">AI 智能写作校对编辑器</p>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li><strong>竞品拆解：</strong>深度对标 Grammarly、ProWritingAid，识别学术科研人员核心痛点。</li>
            <li><strong>核心功能：</strong>设计"分片并发校对"机制，约束 JSON Schema 结构化输出，目标成功率 > 99.5%。</li>
            <li><strong>差异化体验：</strong>首创"上下文聚焦定位"——通过模糊匹配精准溯源并高亮原文。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="project-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <div class="org-group">
              <span class="org">Cure</span>
              <span class="tag">毕业设计</span>
            </div>
            <span class="date">2025 – 2026</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-subtitle">中风患者居家康复可穿戴设备与严肃游戏</p>
          <ul class="bullet-list">
            <li><strong>用户画像：</strong>桌面调研结合实地走访，对3家医院康复科患者进行半结构化访谈。</li>
            <li><strong>解决方案：</strong>基于前沿医学文献挖掘有效训练动作，结合 CV、EMG 技术设计游戏化康复。</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Experience -->
      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">实习经历</h2>
        
        <div class="exp-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <span class="org">北京日报社 · 实习记者</span>
            <span class="date">2024.07 – 2024.08</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-desc">参与国家典籍博物馆“贞观长歌”特展深度报道。独立设计并实现交互式 H5 页面，负责垂直视频内容采编，探索新媒体沉浸式叙事形式。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="exp-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <span class="org">北青深一度训练营 · 法治新闻采编</span>
            <span class="date">2024.03 – 2024.05</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-desc">报道刑事案件，参与法院庭审，采访案件当事人，独立撰写 2 篇深度报道。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="exp-item">
          <div class="item-row">
            <span class="org">北京日报社 · 实习记者</span>
            <span class="date">2023.07 – 2023.10</span>
          </div>
          <p class="item-desc">负责医疗、养老领域新闻采编。发表报道 23 篇，其中 3 篇登载于头版。参与"京城养老大调研"，完成 30+ 户深度访谈。</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Skills -->
      <section class="section last-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">技能与其他</h2>
        <div class="skills-list">
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-label">设计</span>
            <span class="skill-value">Figma, AI, PS, PR, DaVinci, AE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-label">数据</span>
            <span class="skill-value">SPSS, Excel, MySQL, Python</span>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-label">工具</span>
            <span class="skill-value">Obsidian, Antigravity, Claude Code</span>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-row">
            <span class="skill-label">其他</span>
            <span class="skill-value">汕头大学羽毛球校队 · 院级杯男双冠军</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .paper {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* Masthead */
  .masthead {
    padding: 70px 50px 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .masthead-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  .header-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .name {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .photo-wrapper {
    width: 80px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .contact-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
  }

  .contact-divider {
    color: #ccc;
  }

  /* Section */
  .section {
    padding: 35px 50px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .last-section {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #999;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* Items */
  .item-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .org {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .org-group {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 9px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .date {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #999;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .edu-detail, .item-subtitle {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .hl {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .courses, .item-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .link {
    color: #c9463d;
  }

  /* Project & Experience Items */
  .project-item, .exp-item {
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    padding-bottom: 25px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  }

  .project-item:last-child, .exp-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .bullet-list {
    margin: 10px 0 0;
    padding-left: 18px;
  }

  .bullet-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .bullet-list li strong {
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Skills */
  .skills-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .skill-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .skill-label {
    color: #999;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .skill-value {
    color: #666;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .masthead {
      padding: 60px 25px 35px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 30px 25px;
    }

    .header-row {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .item-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .name {
      font-size: 26px;
    }

    .contact-row {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }

  /* Print */
  @media print {
    .page-body { padding-top: 0; }
    .paper { max-width: 100%; }
    .site-nav { display: none; }
  }
</style>
